    <text>
        <body>
            <div type="edition">
                <div type="textpart">
                    <ab><persName key="#Bishops #Popes #Littera/mandatum" ref="#people/51"
                            >Innocentius</persName>
                        <rs key="#Bishops">episcopus</rs>
                        <rs key="#Popes">servus servorum</rs> Dei, venerabili fratri <persName
                            key="#Bishops #Littera/mandatum" ref="#people/3708">Hen[rico</persName>] episcopo et
                        dilectis filiis <rs key="#Consules">consulibus</rs>
                        <placeName key="#Bishops #Consules" ref="#places/7"
                            >Bononiensibus</placeName>, salutem et apostolicam benedictionem.
                        Miramur admodum quoniam, sicut nobis per vestras litteras promisistis,
                        praeda quae per cives vestros dudum <orgName key="#Churches"
                            ref="#juridical_persons/1469"><rs key="#Churches">ecclesiae</rs>
                            <placeName key="#Churches" ref="#places/269">Sancti
                                C[aesarii]</placeName></orgName> facta est eidem loco nondum est,
                        prout accepimus, restituta, quod profecto in nostrum damnum et contunmeliam
                        redundare cognoscitur. Eapropter vos <rs key="#Littera/mandatum">apostolicis
                            litteris</rs> commonentes praecipimus ut, remotis dilationibus, eamdem
                        praedam dilecto filio nostro <persName key="#Abbots" ref="#people/3568"
                            >Henrico</persName>
                        <rs key="#Abbots">abbati</rs>
                        <orgName ref="#juridical_persons/2001" key="#Monasteries #Abbots #Churches"
                            >Sancti Benedicti</orgName> et fratribus eiusdem <rs key="#Monasteries"
                            >monasterii</rs> restitui faciatis et praefatam ecclesiam Sancti
                        C[aesarii] ac bona ad eam pertinentia, sicut eisdem fratribus expedire
                        noveritis, manutenere et adiuvare curetis. Dat(um)
                        <placeName ref="#places/66">Pisis</placeName>, IIII n[onas] iulii. </ab>
                </div>
            </div>
